config BR2_PACKAGE_ROSTEST
	bool "rostest"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_BOOST_SYSTEM
	select BR2_PACKAGE_BOOST_THREAD
	select BR2_PACKAGE_ROSUNIT
	select BR2_PACKAGE_ROS_SET
	help
	  rostest is an extension to roslaunch that enables roslaunch
	  files to be used as test fixtures. As a fully running system
	  has more complex behaviors than an individual ROS node, this
	  allows you to do full integration testing across multiple
	  nodes.

	  http://wiki.ros.org/rostest
